beer.beer_description:
Purple Patch, made in collaboration with GABS, is a showcase of our kettle sour base with an acetic blend for a nostalgic trip to the Corner Store.
We have added Australian Shiraz Grape must and Fresh Boysenberry juice, along with lemon and lime zest and bags of real sherbet and sorbet powder.
Brewed as part of the GABS Summer invitational pack to celebrate the best of an old school Aussie Summer!
